<p>Alleged infiltration and surveillance of human rights organizations. According to the 
information received, various organizations and social movements were subject to 
surveillance and infiltration, namely the Movimento Xingu Vivo para Sempre 
(MXVPS), the Landless Workers&#8217; Movement (Movimiento dos Trabalhadores Rurais 
Sem Terra (MST) as well as the Rede Justi&#231;a nos Trilhos (JnT).  It is reported that the 
