<p><b>Torture;   
</b></p>
<p> 
Alleged practices of solitary confinement and inhuman or degrading conditions in 
detention. According to the information received, between 400 and 500 inmates at the 
United States Penitentiary Administrative Maximum Facility (&#8220;ADX&#8221;) in Florence, 
</p>
<p>Colorado, have been held in prolonged solitary confinement, sometimes for several 
years, and denied adequate medical treatment. It is alleged that these practices cause 
severe physical and mental pain and suffering, which may rise to the level of torture and 
other cruel, inhuman or degrading treatment. 
